verbose_text: In support of these findings, co-injection of pVAX-IL-33 with pVAX-ROP5 + pVAX-ROP18 elicited greater numbers of CD4+ and CD8+ T cells, indicating that this enhanced functionally activated T cells was more beneficial to the development of protective immunity against T. gondii.
